  ESTIMATE='203'
      DESC="iftop does for network usage what top(1) does for CPU usage. 
It listens to network traffic on a named interface and 
displays a table of current bandwidth usage by pairs of 
hosts. Handy for answering the question why is our ADSL 
link so slow?."
